<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8"/>
        <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"/>
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1"/>

        <meta name="description" content="The MS Dev Show is THE podcast for Microsoft developers covering news and topics such as Azure (cloud), Windows, and cross-platform development using MS tools" />
        <meta name="keywords" content="Ms Dev Show,Ms Dev Show Podcast,podcast,Microsoft Dev Show,Microsoft Developer Show,Microsoft" />
        <meta http-equiv="content-language" content="en-us">
        <meta name="application-name" content="MS Dev Show"/>
        <meta name="twitter.site" content="@msdevshow" />
        <meta property="twitter:account_id" content="4503599629427918" />


        <title><%= @getPreparedTitle() %></title>
        <meta name="author" content="<%= @site.author %>">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <link rel="alternate" type="application/rss+xml" title="The MS Dev Show Podcast" href="http://msdevshow.libsyn.com/rss" />
        <link href="/images/favicon.ico?v=2" rel="shortcut icon">

        <!-- Styles -->
        <link href="/styles/site.css" rel="stylesheet" media="screen">

        <!-- HTML5 shim and Respond.js IE8 support of HTML5 elements and media queries -->
        <!--[if lt IE 9]>
        <script src="/scripts/vendor/html5shiv.js"></script>
        <script src="/scripts/vendor/respond.min.js"></script>
        <![endif]-->

        <%- @getBlock('meta').toHTML() %>
        <%- @getBlock('styles').toHTML() %>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div id="container">
            <div id="site-header-container">
                <header id="site-header">
                    <section class="subscribe modal">
                        <label for="modal-1"><div class="btn js-btn">Subscribe</div></label>
                        <div class="modal-window" id="subscribe-dialog">
                            <div class="modal-inner">
                                <label class="modal-close" for="modal-1"></label>
                                <h1>Subscribe!</h1>
                                <ul>
                                    <li><a href="#" title="Subscribe via RSS">RSS</a></li>
                                    <li><a href="#" title="Subscribe via Windows Phone">Windows Phone</a></li>
                                    <li><a href="#" title="Subscribe via iTunes">iTunes</a></li>
                                    <li><a href="#" title="Subscribe via Stitcher">Stitcher</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <aside id="header-logo">
                        <a href="/">
                            <img src="/images/logo@2x.png" alt="MS Dev Show Logo" title="The Microsoft Developer Show Podcast" />
                        </a>
                    </aside>

                    <section class="search-bar">
                        <div class="search-and-submit">
                            <form class="navbar-form navbar-right hidden-xs" role="search" action="http://bing.com/search" method="get">
                              <input type="search" name="q" placeholder="Search" />
                              <input type="hidden" name="q" value="site:msdevshow.com">
                              <button type="submit">
                                <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/thoughtbot/refills/master/source/images/search-icon.png" alt="Search Icon">
                              </button>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                </header>
            </div>
            <%- @content %>
            <div id="site-footer-container">
                <footer id="site-footer">
                    <section id="footer-colophon">
                        <h1>About the MS Dev Show</h1>
                        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Suspendisse sit amet orci cursus, vehicula sapien at, vehicula magna. Duis dui nisi, ultrices sit amet aliquet et, consequat vulputate lacus. Donec varius semper dictum. Sed quis malesuada lectus. Sed malesuada risus id gravida ullamcorper. Sed in velit convallis, elementum purus quis, dignissim dolor. Nam dictum nibh id nisl porttitor, sit amet pellentesque ante facilisis. </p>
                    </section>
                    <nav id="footer-navigation">
                        <div class="footer-nav">
                            <h1><a href="#">Archives</a></h1>
                            <p>See our past shows!</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="footer-nav">
                            <h1><a href="#">Subscribe</a></h1>
                            <p>We're available everywhere; subscribe through any of these sources:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>iTunes</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="footer-nav">
                            <h1><a href="#">Guests</a></h1>
                            <p>Want to talk on the air? Contact us!</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="footer-nav">
                            <h1><a href="#">Sponsors</a></h1>
                            <p>We're in the beginning phases of sponsorship. If you or your company are interested, reach out to us!</p>
                        </div>
                    </nav>
                </footer>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Scripts -->

        <%- @getBlock('scripts').toHTML() %>
        <script src="//ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
        <script src="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.1.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
        <!--<script src="/scripts/site.js"></script>-->

        <script>
          (function(i,s,o,g,r,a,m){i['GoogleAnalyticsObject']=r;i[r]=i[r]||function(){
          (i[r].q=i[r].q||[]).push(arguments)},i[r].l=1*new Date();a=s.createElement(o),
          m=s.getElementsByTagName(o)[0];a.async=1;a.src=g;m.parentNode.insertBefore(a,m)
          })(window,document,'script','//www.google-analytics.com/analytics.js','ga');

          ga('create', 'UA-342471-11', 'msdevshow.com');
          ga('send', 'pageview');

        </script>

        <!-- /Scripts -->
    </body>
</html>